Enclosing class:
TextEditor
public static class TextEditor.NewFileRequestEvent extends Event
Custom event for requesting new file operations. This event is fired when the user presses Ctrl+N or uses other new file shortcuts. Parent components can listen for this event to handle new file creation appropriately.
